 role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614840\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614840\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nnl1665703077577.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nnl1665703077577.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nnl1665703077577.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nnl1665703077577\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Entity Color (\n                              EntColor)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the widget inherits the foreground and background color of the entity. <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>. Deprecated. Use <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherit Colors</span> instead.\n   </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__p_d103358e1_d103359e1_d103360e1\">EntColor<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__section_ihf_gl3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d889958e76\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__table_d12194e1_d12195e1_d12196e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes \n              </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__section_jgw_3l3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d889958e125\">Description</h2>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__note_dzr_ll3_wwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherit Colors</span> property is\n        available for more widgets than <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">EntColor</span> and defaults to the Windows\n        system color. However, for compatibility reasons, when <code class=\"ph codeph\">EntColor=True</code>, it\n        takes precedence over the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherit Colors</span> property. This can result in\n        an inconsistent appearance. We therefore recommend that you use <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherit\n          Colors</span> rather than <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">EntColor</span>.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__p_d103367e1_d103368e1_d103369e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">EntColor</span> is True:</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__ol_ixl_nl3_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">The edit box inherits the color of the entity.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">If no color is defined for the entity, the visible color is inherited from the parent\n          frame or a form.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">If no color is defined for the parent, the visible color of the parent is used, not the\n          Windows default color for edit boxes. This is in contrast to the behavior of the\n            <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherit Colors</span> property. </li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__p_d103370e1_d103371e1_d103372e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bjj1665702873773.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bjj1665702873773.html\" title=\"It is possible to explicitly define background and foreground colors for most objects. If you do not explicitly define a color, the actual color used depends on the type of object, and on the Inherit Colors and Transparency properties (where applicable).\">Color Inheritance</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nnl1665703077577__section_qsh_rl3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d889958e190\">Applies to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Index Color</a><p>Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bjj1665702873773.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Color Inheritance</a><p>It is possible to explicitly define background and foreground colors for most objects. If you do not explicitly define a color, the actual color used depends on the type of object, and on the Inherit Colors and Transparency properties (where applicable).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcv1665702609942.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Inherit Colors (InheritColors)</a><p>Determines whether the background and foreground colors of the parent entity or form can be inherited. This property can be set in ProcScript for the widgets, but not for labels. Valid Values are True or False (default).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614840\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614840\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Entity Color ( EntColor) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Entity Color ( EntColor) Determines whether the widget inherits the foreground and background color of the entity. True (default) or False . Deprecated. Use Inherit Colors instead. EntColor = \" True | False \" Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? Yes Dependencies: None Description Note: The Inherit Colors property is available for more widgets than EntColor and defaults to the Windows system color. However, for compatibility reasons, when EntColor=True , it takes precedence over the Inherit Colors property. This can result in an inconsistent appearance. We therefore recommend that you use Inherit Colors rather than EntColor . When EntColor is True: The edit box inherits the color of the entity. If no color is defined for the entity, the visible color is inherited from the parent frame or a form. If no color is defined for the parent, the visible color of the parent is used, not the Windows default color for edit boxes. This is in contrast to the behavior of the Inherit Colors property. For more information, see Color Inheritance . Applies to EditBox Related Links Index Color Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated. Color Inheritance It is possible to explicitly define background and foreground colors for most objects. If you do not explicitly define a color, the actual color used depends on the type of object, and on the Inherit Colors and Transparency properties (where applicable). Inherit Colors (InheritColors) Determines whether the background and foreground colors of the parent entity or form can be inherited. This property can be set in ProcScript for the widgets, but not for labels. Valid Values are True or False (default). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}